                        <additions>
                            <list> 
                                <item xml:id="a1">
                                    <locus target="#1v"/>
                                    <desc type="OwnershipNote">The note states that the manuscript belongs to the church of 
                                        <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/INS0101MadhaneAlam">Madḫāne ʿAlam</placeName>
                                    </desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">ምሳሌያተ፡ ሰሎሞን፡ ዘመድኃኔ፡ አለም።</q>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a2">
                                    <locus target="#21v"/>
                                    <desc type="GuestText">A short account of the Prophets, beginning with Job:</desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">ነገረ፡ ትንቢቶሙ፡ ለነቢያት። ቀዳማይ፡ ኢዮብ፡ ተነበየ፡ 
                                        ፵ዓመተ፡ ወእምድኅሬሁ፡ ሙሴ፡ ተነበየ፡ ፵ዓመተ፡ ቅድመ፡ ልደተ፡ እግዚእነ፡
                                        በሥጋ፡ ፲ወ፬፻፱ወ፭ዓመት ፤ etc.</q>
                                    <desc>Then follow various chronological data:</desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">እስከ፡ አይኅ፡ ኮነ፡ ዓመት፡ ፳፻ወ፪፻፵ወ፪ዓመት ፤ እምአብርሃም፡ እስከ፡ ጸዓተ፡ 
                                        እስራኤል፡ እምግብፅ፡ ፬፻ወ፴፩ዓመት፤ etc.</q>
                                    <desc>down to ʿAlamīd, concluding as follows:</desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">ወእምዓለሚድ፡ እስከ፡ ሣልስ፡ መንግሥተ፡ 
                                        አሮዌ፡ ፸ወ፯ዓመት፡ ወ፯አውራኅ ፤ ወሲሳዩ፡ ለአር ዌ ፤ 
                                        ዘዕለት፡ ፲አስዋር፡ ወ፲አልሕምት፡ ፫፻ ዓባግዕ ፤ ፫፻አጣሌ፡ ወትዕሊፊተ፡ 
                                        (sic) አዕላፋት፡ አዕዋፍ፡ ወአሐቲ፡ ወለት፡ ዮንግልት ፤ ወቀሙ፡ ፸በዕመት፡ ወግድሙ፡ ፳ወስነኒሁ፡ ፩በዕመት።</q>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a3">
                                    <locus target="#47v"/>
                                    <desc type="GuestText">
                                        <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3852KingList">King list (general record)</title>
                                        Lists of kings of Judah and <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC3937Israel">Israel</placeName>, 
                                        the Prophets, and the High-priests.
                                    </desc>
                                    
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a4">
                                    <locus target="#48r"/>
                                    <desc type="GuestText">
                                        Explanation of Hebrew words:
                                        <q xml:lang="gez">ትርጓሜ፡ ዘእብራይስጥ፡ ውስተ፡ ግዕዝ ፤ ኤሎሄ፡ ብሂል፡ አምላክ። አዶይ፡ (sic) 
                                            ብሂል፡ እግዚእ ፤ ጸባኦት፡ ብሂል፡ ዘኃይላት፤ etc.</q>
                                    </desc>
                                    
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a5">
                                    <locus target="#48r"/>
                                    <desc type="GuestText">
                                        A statement on the number of the Kings of Israel, the sum-total of their years, etc.
                                        
                                    </desc>
                                                                        
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a6">
                                    <locus target="#48r"/>
                                    <desc type="GuestText">A piece entitled <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/NAR0012temple">ምሳሌ፡ ቤተ፡ መቅደስ፡</title> or <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/NAR0012temple">Comparison of the 
                                        Temple</title>
                                        , beginning
                                        <q xml:lang="gez">ቀዳማዊ፡ መደብ፡ ይትሜሰል፡ በምድር። ወካልዕ፡ መደብ፡ ይት፡ በገነት ፤ ወሣልስ፡ 
                                            መ፡ ይ፡ በጠፈር ፤ ወራብዕ፡ መ፡ ይ፡ በአርያም ፤ etc.</q>
                                    </desc>
                                    
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a7">
                                    <locus target="#48v"/>
                                    <desc type="GuestText">A list of the various alphabets 
                                        or modes of writing
                                        <q xml:lang="gez">ሀለዉ፡ መጻሕፍት፡ ዘኍልቆሙ፡ ፳፡ ፰ዘቤተ፡ ሴም፡ ዘ ውእቶሙ፡ ዐረቢ፡ ሶርያዊ፡ 
                                            አዢዕብራዊ፡ (sic) ፋርሳዊ፡ ከለደዊ፡ ህንዲ፡ ሲኒ፡ ወለቤተ፡ 
                                            ካም፡ ፯፡ ቅብጢ፡ ኖቢ፡ ሐበሺ፡ ቂልቂ፡ ፍልስጢኒ፡ ቁብኒ፡ ወለቤተ፡ ያፌት፡ 
                                             ፯ዮናኒ፡ ሮሚዊ፡ አርማንያዊ፡ አፍርንጋዊ፡ ጌርጋኒ፡ እንልሲ።</q>
                                        and a list of words explained in Amharic.
                                    </desc>
                                    
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a9">
                                    <locus target="#1v"/>
                                    
                                    <desc type="Gloss">A list of words (not Ethiopic) 
                                        glossed in Amharic, but for the most part 
                                        indistinctly written.
                                        <q xml:lang="am">ሚርጔ፡ ዘቀኝ፡ ሲታ፡ ዘግራ፡ ዓልቴ፡ ዘ፡ ዋልህ፡ ቡልቴ፡
                                            አደርህ፡ ያዴ፡ ዘ፡ ናፈቀ፡ ሐደት፡ ዘ፡ አሰበ፡ ነገደ፡ ዘ፡ እንት፡ አለህ፡ etc.</q>
                                    </desc>
                                    
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a10">
                                    <locus target="#1r"/>
                                    
                                    <desc type="GuestText">the first sūra of the 
                                        <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1089alQura">Qurʾān</ref>, rudely written in Arabic.
                                        <q xml:lang="ar"/>
                                    </desc>
                                    
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a11">
                                    <locus from="44r" to="46v"/>
                                    
                                    <desc type="Gloss">Song of Songs is copiously glossed, cp. also <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BLorient495#a5">BL orient 495</ref>.
                                    </desc>
                                    
                                </item>
                            </list>
                        </additions>
